StyleGAN of All Trades:Image Manipulation with Only Pretrained StyleGAN 论文笔记

Posted on 2021-11-12

Introduction

继noise space Z， disentanglement intermediate latent space W，加入level信息的W+，affine transformed后的S之后，终于有人甚至对feature space动手了，这系列研究做到最后是不是要直接用Photoshop对image进行manipulation了？（手动狗头）

作者将manipulation放到抽象层次仅次于pixel space的feature space之后，又多了很多新的玩法，效果都还行

Motivation

出发点就一个，作者发现以往的image manipulation和editing的tasks：

Most methods either are designed in a task-specific manner or require additional architectures.

作者想要证明：

A vanilla StyleGAN is sufficient to host a variety of different tasks.

方法也非常地Vanilla：

By exploiting the spatial properties of the intermediate layers along with some simple operations.

Proposed Method

作者讲到自己主要用了Suzuki et al.的方法

Perform collaging in the intermediate spatial feature space of GANs

一张图说明作者的method

直接在feature space进行operation，胆子也是真的肥。针对不同的任务，有些微调，下面分别介绍:

Feature Interpolation

这里就是说Suzuki et al的方法

This collaging does not work well when the images to be blended are too different.

于是作者用了interpolation：

其中，fi表示i-th layer的intermediate features，

α是一个mask，表示在spatial上想要如何interpolating两个feature。

Generation from a single image

想和SinGAN掰一掰手腕，因为StyleGAN是full-convolution结构，所以支持任意维度的feature input，那么：

In some feature layers, we select relevant patches and replicate it spatially by blending it with other regions.

方法是：

用这种方法，也能生成diverse的image，只是需要

manual choosing of patches for feature interpolation

除此之外，还能进行image extention：

The extension of our method based on reflection padding generates realistic textures that are structurally sound.

Improved GAN inversion

说了W+ code的一个局限：

the resulting style codes often fall into unstable out-of-domain regions of the space, making it difficult to perform any semantic control over the resulting images.

所以想要将image给inverse到style space S，但也没说具体方法。就提了一句：

We discover that the S space without any transformations can also be modeled as Gaussian distribution. We are then able to impose the same Gaussian prior in this space instead during GAN inversion.

就理解成，现在inverse到S空间就行了。

Controllable I2I translation

跟toonify的思路一样，估计也是完成类似的task：

  1. First finetune FFHQ-pretrained StyleGAN on the target dataset(e.g., Disney)
  2. Perform weight swapping for I2I

而这里，因为用到了feature interpolation，其中mask α，既可以continuous地控制，也可以对local region进行控制。

Panorama Generation

有一点新的task，还是feature interpolation的思路

Using feature interpolation, we can blend two side-by-side images by creating a realistic transition that connects them.

这个process大概是这样：

其实问题就是，两张图进行connect，可能因为差距太大而效果不好，所以作者用了一个latent smoothing：

applying a Gaussian filter across latent codes(intermediate feature) to smooth neighboring latent codes.

并且：

perform feature interpolation at every single layer.

Attributes Transfer

作者说一些方法要么highly dependent on pose and orientation，要么not ensure that irrelevant regions are not affected。主要为了解决pose的问题，作者提出一个pose alignment的方法：

We can simly align the first 2048 dimensions of the W+ space style code between the source and reference images.

然后再进行feature interpolation。

Discussion

作者还说自己用到了

only pretrained StyleGAN models along with spatial operations on the latent space.

都快到pixel space了还在那latent space呢。
